#: ../../docs/training_manual/database_concepts/adding_data.rst:78
msgid ""
"Recall that in this example, we defined phone numbers as strings, not "
"integers."
msgstr ""
"Kom ihåg att vi i det här exemplet definierade telefonnummer som strängar, "
"inte heltal."

